talent 1

5 armor 80 movement and 200 life

talent 2

15 damage 10 attackspeed and 100 cast range



PASSIVE F OR D Thief Soul
increase overall stats

damage 3 5 7 9
attackspeed 4 8 12 16
allstats 2 3 4 5
magic resist 3% 5% 7%
spellvamp 4% 8%
every item riki got, it will increase is agility by 2 and life by 10

talent level 25 upgrade Thief Soul
double all stats
increase the agility gain by 1 of item and life by 10

add a new modifier Deadly
if riki attack the same target 4 time in a row the next attack get 100% increase damage
and deal pure damage cooldown 3


SPELL Q Dagger Strike -NOTE- all riki spell and passive will deal damage base on this total basic attack damage
deal damage and reducing the enemy damage and attack speed for a short duration and after dealing the damage, the dagger
will bounce up to 4 target doing less damage and also reducing damage but not attackspeed

Attack damage 130% 150% 170% 190%
damage reduction 15% 20% 25% 30%
attack speed lost 10 15 20 25
bouncing dagger damage 110% 120% 130% 140%
bouncing dagger damage reduction 5% 10% 15% 20%
debuff duration 3 second
mana cost 100 plus 2% of max mana
cooldown 8

talent level 10 upgrade Dagger Strike
increase damage by 30%
increase damage reduction by 5%
reduce mana cost by 50
reduce cooldown by 2

add a new modifier Poison Dagger
after striking the enemy, he will get poison dealing 8 pure damage per second and disabling regeneration for 3 second
also increase the damage he take by anything by 15%


SPELL W Blink Stab
jump behind the enemy stunning them and dealing damage, after the stun the target get silence.

Attack damage 125% 160% 195% 230%
stun 0.60 0.65 0.70 0.75
stun increase by 0.01 per agility point
silence 1.30 1.40 1.50 1.60
silence increase by 0.02 per agility point
mana cost 150 plus 1% of max mana
cooldown 16 14 12 10

talent level 10 upgrade Blink Stab
increase damage by 25%
increase stun by 0.15
increase silence by 0.40
cost no mana

add a new modifier Stab Feast
after blinking on the target riki get 25% increase damage and 15% of is damage become pure for 3 second, if any
enemy die by blink stab riki will get heal for 10% of is max life


